7.51</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; Charondas <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πρῶτος ἐποίησε τὴν ἐ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg035.perseus-grc1:1274b:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pol.\">Pol.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1274b7</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τούτων</foreign> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰς ἐ. εἶναι</foreign> theirs shall be the right of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐ.</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg047.perseus-grc1:72\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">47.72</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}